ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing Minister of Indigenous Services to Transfer, Lease or Loan Public Property to Support Public Health Emergency Management
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Indigenous Services to TRANSFER, LEASE, OR LOAN, to any government, body, organization or person in Canada, any public property — including masks, personal protective equipment, food, medication, drugs, vaccines, chemicals, ventilators, medical and testing devices, freezers and temporary emergency health infrastructure — that is necessary to support public health emergency management.
